Naruto delivers a string of punches and kicks using shadow clones. The penultimate of these attacks are enhanced with [[natural energy]], which stuns his opponent. Naruto then jumps at his opponent and kicks them down, bouncing off them, going up high, and comes crashing down with a Rasengan.
